41:34.200 --> 41:34.920
Oma Yu

41:36.800 --> 41:37.520
Oma Yu

41:50.680 --> 41:51.360
Oma Yu

41:51.880 --> 41:52.640
Oma Yu

41:53.600 --> 41:54.280
Xiaolan

41:54.960 --> 41:55.720
Xiaolan

